// QUESTION BANKS
//   PRACTICE_POOL (246) — 6 distinct 40-Q exams (EXAM_SETS, zero overlap) + topic + adaptive
//   MOCK_POOL (100)      — reserved, never shown in practice (held-out mock exams)
